{
  "id": "69b4737eb658e217828ed148",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:デザイン思考",
  "created": 1773433761,
  "updated": 1773433796,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b4737eb658e217828ed148",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:デザイン思考",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433761,
      "updated": 1773433761
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a00000000000a9d0ff",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433761,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d100",
      "text": "はーい！今日は「[デザイン思考]」についてゆるっと語る回だよ〜！🎮✨",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d101",
      "text": "なんか名前だけ聞くと「デザイナーの思考？」って感じだけど、実は問題の解決のしかたみたいなやつなんだよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d102",
      "text": "ユーザーの気持ちをめっちゃ考えてアイデア出す感じ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d103",
      "text": "りか、テック担当として軽く説明よろ〜！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d104",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d105",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d106",
      "text": "了解。簡潔に説明する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d107",
      "text": "[** デザイン思考（Design Thinking）]とは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d108",
      "text": "「ユーザー中心で問題を発見し、試作と改善を繰り返す問題解決プロセス」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d109",
      "text": "一般的には次の5ステップが有名。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d10a",
      "text": " 1. Empathize（共感） – ユーザーを理解する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d10b",
      "text": " 2. Define（定義） – 問題を整理する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d10c",
      "text": " 3. Ideate（発想） – アイデアを出す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d10d",
      "text": " 4. Prototype（試作） – とりあえず作る",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d10e",
      "text": " 5. Test（検証） – ユーザーに試してもらう",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d10f",
      "text": "スタンフォード大学のd.schoolが広めた方法論として知られている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d110",
      "text": "参考:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d111",
      "text": "https://dschool.stanford.edu/resources/getting-started-with-design-thinking",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d112",
      "text": "要点。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d113",
      "text": " ユーザー中心",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d114",
      "text": " 小さく作って早く試す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d115",
      "text": " 何度も改善する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d116",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d117",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d118",
      "text": "おお〜！まとめ助かる🙏",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d119",
      "text": "つまりあれだよね、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d11a",
      "text": "「頭で考えすぎる前に、とりあえず作ってみるゲー」って感じ？ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d11b",
      "text": "ゲーム開発とかでもあるよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d11c",
      "text": "「仮で作ったら意外と神仕様だった」みたいなやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d11d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d11e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d11f",
      "text": "（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d120",
      "text": "その説明、とても愛らしいですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d121",
      "text": "確かに、思索の机の上だけでは、人の心は見えてきませんものね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d122",
      "text": "本の物語でもそうですが、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d123",
      "text": "登場人物の心に寄り添うことで物語が生まれるように、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d124",
      "text": "デザイン思考もまた、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d125",
      "text": "人の体験に耳を澄ませることから始まるのでしょうね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d126",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d127",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d128",
      "text": "その理解は本質的。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d129",
      "text": "デザイン思考のコアは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d12a",
      "text": "Human-Centered Design（人間中心設計）。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d12b",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d12c",
      "text": ">「技術が何を作れるか」ではなく",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d12d",
      "text": ">「人が何を必要としているか」から考える。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d12e",
      "text": "これは工学の世界でも重要なパラダイムシフトだった。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d12f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d130",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d131",
      "text": "あ〜それわかる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d132",
      "text": "例えばさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d133",
      "text": "「すごい機能のアプリ！」って作っても、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d134",
      "text": "使いにくかったら秒でアンインストールじゃん？📱",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d135",
      "text": "ユーザー「わかんねぇ…」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d136",
      "text": "→はい終了ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d137",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d138",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d139",
      "text": "正確。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d13a",
      "text": "多くのプロダクトが失敗する理由の一つは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d13b",
      "text": "[** Problem-Solution Fit（問題と解決の適合）]がないこと。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d13c",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d13d",
      "text": "「解く価値のある問題か？」を確認していない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d13e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d13f",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d140",
      "text": "なるほど……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d141",
      "text": "それはまるで、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d142",
      "text": "誰も困っていないことを一生懸命に助けようとしてしまうようなものですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d143",
      "text": "優しさはあるけれど、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d144",
      "text": "相手の事情を知らなければ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d145",
      "text": "本当に必要な手助けにはならない……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d146",
      "text": "（少し考える）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d147",
      "text": "デザイン思考とは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d148",
      "text": "まず相手の物語を読むことなのかもしれませんね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d149",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d14a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d14b",
      "text": "あや、それ文学的すぎてちょいエモいんだけど🥹",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d14c",
      "text": "でもマジでそう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d14d",
      "text": "「ユーザーの物語を読む」って表現、神。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d14e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d14f",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d150",
      "text": "補足する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d151",
      "text": "デザイン思考では、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d152",
      "text": "ユーザーインタビューや観察を重視する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d153",
      "text": "理由はシンプル。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d154",
      "text": "人は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d155",
      "text": "「自分の問題を正確に言語化できない」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d156",
      "text": "ことが多いから。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d157",
      "text": "だから",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d158",
      "text": " 行動を観察",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d159",
      "text": " 体験を分析",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d15a",
      "text": "する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d15b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d15c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d15d",
      "text": "あーわかる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d15e",
      "text": "「何が不便ですか？」って聞かれても",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d15f",
      "text": "「うーん…別に…」ってなるやつｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d160",
      "text": "でも実際触ってると",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d161",
      "text": "めっちゃ迷ってるみたいな。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d162",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d163",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d164",
      "text": "（静かに笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d165",
      "text": "確かにそのような場面、よくありますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d166",
      "text": "人の言葉は、ときに遠慮や習慣に包まれてしまいます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d167",
      "text": "ですが、行動は正直です。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d168",
      "text": "ですから",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d169",
      "text": "その人の一日をそっと観察することが、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d16a",
      "text": "真実への道になるのでしょう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d16b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d16c",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d16d",
      "text": "ここで一度、要点を整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d16e",
      "text": "デザイン思考の核心",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d16f",
      "text": "1. ユーザーへの共感",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d170",
      "text": "2. 問題の再定義",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d171",
      "text": "3. 自由なアイデア発想",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d172",
      "text": "4. 高速プロトタイピング",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d173",
      "text": "5. ユーザーテスト",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d174",
      "text": "重要なのは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d175",
      "text": "線形ではなく、何度もループすること。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d176",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d177",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d178",
      "text": "つまりRPGでいうと",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d179",
      "text": "「仮装備でボス挑む",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d17a",
      "text": "↓",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d17b",
      "text": "ボコられる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d17c",
      "text": "↓",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d17d",
      "text": "装備変える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d17e",
      "text": "↓",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d17f",
      "text": "また挑む」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d180",
      "text": "みたいな感じ？🎮",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d181",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d182",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d183",
      "text": "……近い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d184",
      "text": "それは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d185",
      "text": "[** イテレーション（反復改善）]の概念。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d186",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d187",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d188",
      "text": "（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d189",
      "text": "失敗を恥ずかしがらず、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d18a",
      "text": "少しずつ良い形に近づいていくのですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d18b",
      "text": "それはまるで、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d18c",
      "text": "推敲を重ねて文章を磨く作家の営みにも似ています。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d18d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d18e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d18f",
      "text": "おお〜！確かに。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d190",
      "text": "1回で神作品とか無理だもんね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d191",
      "text": "β版→アップデート→神ゲーみたいな流れ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d192",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d193",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d194",
      "text": "最後に重要なポイントを一つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d195",
      "text": "デザイン思考は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d196",
      "text": "デザイナーだけのものではない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d197",
      "text": "ビジネス、教育、ソフトウェア開発など",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d198",
      "text": "多くの分野で使われている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d199",
      "text": "例",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d19a",
      "text": " IDEO",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d19b",
      "text": " Google",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d19c",
      "text": " IBM",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d19d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d19e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d19f",
      "text": "つまり今日のまとめ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1a0",
      "text": "デザイン思考は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1a1",
      "text": "🧠「人の気持ちを理解する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1a2",
      "text": "💡「アイデア出しまくる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1a3",
      "text": "🛠「とりあえず作る」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1a4",
      "text": "🔁「ダメなら直す」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1a5",
      "text": "このループ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1a6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1a7",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1a8",
      "text": "ええ、とても素敵な考え方ですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1a9",
      "text": "人を理解しようとする姿勢から、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1aa",
      "text": "新しいものが生まれる……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1ab",
      "text": "それは、技術の世界であっても、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1ac",
      "text": "どこか温かい営みに感じられます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1ad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1ae",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1af",
      "text": "同意。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1b0",
      "text": "結論。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773433762,
      "updated": 1773433762
    },
    {
      "id": "69b473a10000000000a9d1b1",
      "text": "良いデザインとは、",
